{"tid":1333438,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"啱啱朋友講左啲說話，我覺得好難受。","createTime":"2019-07-19T16:36:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-19T17:00:23.000Z","uid":241586,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c04dbfda9b878789733ed64a820d4d75e6304285","tid":1333438,"uid":241586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T16:36:45.000Z","msg":"同朋友傾開計<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />聽到啲難聽過粗口嘅嘢。<br />\n背景係朋友喺沙田翻緊Part-time<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：朋友 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：我<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：聽講班示威者聽日又遊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />搞還搞，六點後先好搞<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 點解要6點後？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：吓？我計時薪㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢地搞事咪姐係我又要早收，又揾少左？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：其實你知唔知根本就唔係班示威者搞事，係班黑警。<br />\n<br />\n之後朋友冇再出聲，但我都冇解釋同再發佢脾氣。<br />\n<br />\n我好失望，真係好失望。我地係好多年嘅好朋友，<br />\n我好錫佢，我地好少嘈交。<br />\n但今日佢講嘅嘢我真係好心up好難受。<br />\n<br />\n出面成百萬人為你上街，為你抗爭。<br />\n要比人打，要比人噴，仲要比你地抹黑唾罵。<br />\n佢地仲要係為左你，一蚊都冇得收，日日上街，日曬雨淋，比警棍毆打，用槍威脅。<br />\n每一個人，頭破血流都要上街。<br />\n我好想知，喺你心目中，嗰幾條人命，嗰啲流血犧牲嘅人，又係咪真係咁一文不值。<br />\n<br />\n我好痛啊個心<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真係好撚痛<br />\n我唔敢要求你清醒<br />\n我只係想你可以有翻啲血性，唔好再講風涼說話。<br />\n<br />\n利申: 6月9號叫朋友上街佢話約左人唔想改期 到依家都冇一日出過黎<br />\n<br />\n有冇人可以教我點面對佢？"},{"pid":"b222b0eb97d190d60646d6fc36fbde9f1b5b0d4c","tid":1333438,"uid":11804,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T16:38:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ec208b3dd0a36b3413824d1a8e629504a2ada72e","tid":1333438,"uid":171273,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T16:43:22.000Z","msg":"唔好話咩為佢爭取<br />\n佢呢啲人自願放棄自己與生俱來嘅權利<br />\n我哋做咩要為佢爭取<br />\n我哋係為同路人爭取<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3446e7f236ed43cc0f8643f3076867013366c5aa","tid":1333438,"uid":202224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T16:44:48.000Z","msg":"唔緊要 做普通朋友"},{"pid":"fc0546cfbdd8edd99d512b0db86df1dde6e1c601","tid":1333438,"uid":56323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T16:57:46.000Z","msg":"道不同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d31d9813766d464b7570145787dee3783df3890","tid":1333438,"uid":263730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T17:00:23.000Z","msg":"返part time都咁緊張份糧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}